  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>**This game is no longer being supported by updates, but it's now free to play!</strong>**</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099280/extras/60c626b84d3523a764fc7dcec4d87dbe.poster.avif?t=1745344414\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099280/extras/60c626b84d3523a764fc7dcec4d87dbe.webm?t=1745344414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099280/extras/60c626b84d3523a764fc7dcec4d87dbe.mp4?t=1745344414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Metro Manager LA is a strategy simulation game about connecting communities throughout Los Angeles. Manage maintenance, security, wait time, and train capacity as you attempt to keep the riders of Los Angeles happy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099280/extras/d67b06405e27c829457ae74b77381251.poster.avif?t=1745344414\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099280/extras/d67b06405e27c829457ae74b77381251.webm?t=1745344414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099280/extras/d67b06405e27c829457ae74b77381251.mp4?t=1745344414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Connect over 50 real communities around the Los Angeles area.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Shuffle workers around your stations and trains to respond to maintenance and crime as it arises.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Add new cars to an existing train to increase capacity on popular lines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unlock new trains to ensure low wait times for your riders</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Complete in-demand routes to claim rewards and keep your riders happy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099280/extras/5a725087c8b6c30ad6c115dfabcd142e.poster.avif?t=1745344414\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099280/extras/5a725087c8b6c30ad6c115dfabcd142e.webm?t=1745344414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099280/extras/5a725087c8b6c30ad6c115dfabcd142e.mp4?t=1745344414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>**This game is no longer being supported by updates, but it's now free to play!</strong>**</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099280/extras/60c626b84d3523a764fc7dcec4d87dbe.poster.avif?t=1745344414\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099280/extras/60c626b84d3523a764fc7dcec4d87dbe.webm?t=1745344414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099280/extras/60c626b84d3523a764fc7dcec4d87dbe.mp4?t=1745344414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Metro Manager LA is a strategy simulation game about connecting communities throughout Los Angeles. Manage maintenance, security, wait time, and train capacity as you attempt to keep the riders of Los Angeles happy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099280/extras/d67b06405e27c829457ae74b77381251.poster.avif?t=1745344414\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099280/extras/d67b06405e27c829457ae74b77381251.webm?t=1745344414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099280/extras/d67b06405e27c829457ae74b77381251.mp4?t=1745344414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Connect over 50 real communities around the Los Angeles area.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Shuffle workers around your stations and trains to respond to maintenance 